snippet.title: Rusty's Day Off: Episode One - Janitor on Duty (Announcement Trailer)
snippet.description:
Rusty's Day Off is a stylized puzzle-shooter in which you play as a janitor caught up in a wild adventure on his day off. Armed with your gadgets, you must navigate through complex facilities, solve puzzles, defeat rogue robots and jump & run your way through this day.
